  "records": {
    "description": "Designed for quad displays, with all wiring up top. Hopperlocking is possible with a dustline above the dispenser.\n\n**Features:**\n- Automatic box replacement when emptied\n- Global first box placement",
    "considerations": [
      "Full boxes will buffer in the hopper and dispenser"
    ],
    "notes": "For 1.11+ compatibility replace the glass with slabs/solid blocks and noteblocks with trapdoors/rails."
  },
